

### Arguments

| Name | Type | Description | Required |
|----------|------|-------------|----------|

### Returns

[`number`](/docs/kcl/types/std-types-number)


### Examples

```kcl
exampleSketch = startSketchOn(XZ)
  |> startProfile(at = [0, 0])
  |> angledLine(
    angle = 50,
    length = sqrt(2500),
```
